##{title:}##

A number of data formats have been considered for the long-term storage of the
blog entries; main driving force behind this was the need to have the contents
stored away in a manner which is decoupled from a specific tool responsible for
the rendering of the contents into HTML pages of typeset documents.

### XML schema ###

~~~
<entry>
  <title></title>
  <date></date>
  <author></author>
  <tags>
    <tag></tag>
    <tag></tag>
  </tags>
  <body></body>
</entry>
~~~
